Cell[TextData[{
 "Note that the Bell states can be generated from the logical basis states by \
the so-called quantum entangler circuit, a combination of the Hadamard gate \
and the CNOT gate discussed in ",
 ButtonBox["Two-Qubit Gates",
  BaseStyle->"Link",
  ButtonData->"paclet:QuantumMob/Q3/tutorial/TwoQubitGates#1585062394"],
 ". Therefore, the Bell measurement can be achieved by applying the inverse \
of the entangling operation."
}], "TechNoteText",
 CellID->187727384,ExpressionUUID->"a9fa6e41-7751-459d-b9ce-9d1eacfbf1ee"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

