Cell["\<\
Observe that the disentangler quantum circuit indeed maps the Bell states \
into the logical basis states.\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->1013935962,ExpressionUUID->"cc4555cd-5c9e-494d-8430-fc6dfe191faf"],

